# Cloudflare Pages redirects + SPA fallback.
# Copied from dist/_redirects after `expo export -p web`.

# Canonicalize www → apex so Google indexes one version, not two.
https://www.byheadless.com/*  https://byheadless.com/:splat  301!

# SPA fallback: known routes (e.g. /login, /signup) are served as their
# pre-rendered .html first; only unmatched paths (like dynamic /[siteId]/...)
# fall back to index.html so the client-side router can resolve them.
/*  /index.html  200
